ption key，亦即係熄機，掹電芯，跟住希望你事前加密功夫足夠，同埋你嘅心理質素能夠抵受到折磨。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T08:41:43.000Z","msg":"消磁都無用？<br />\n手機直接沖廁所/粉碎<br />\n<br />\n我係做曬都信唔過自己set嘅加密<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb2c51682cec093d9bc3fb3a0ef3f004b58ae10b","tid":1956324,"uid":131691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"665feb7a82390065ec9b3d7dac40bf81701436df","tid":1956324,"uid":236414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8cbe273268360ffd3b61b484c7a090c071c82952","tid":1956324,"uid":131691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5ee081649d86a46ead116d8b2718b48be4194fb4","tid":1956324,"uid":236414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T08:05:42.000Z","msg":"點睇wickr?<br />\n<br />\n危急起黎要銷毀電腦我寧願物理破壞好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T08:17:31.000Z","msg":"物理破壞係冇用㗎，你就算用電鑽去鑽個harddisk都可以recover<br />\n危急起嚟淨係可以做一樣嘢：丟棄encryption key，亦即係熄機，掹電芯，跟住希望你事前加密功夫足夠，同埋你嘅心理質素能夠抵受到折磨。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T08:41:43.000Z","msg":"消磁都無用？<br />\n手機直接沖廁所/粉碎<br />\n<br />\n我係做曬都信唔過自己set嘅加密<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T08:49:12.000Z","msg":"磁石真心冇用，微波爐都係<br />\n沖落廁所其實還好，但係最重要係你要熄機"},{"pid":"dc61437b47771dcd74dafd8554bf57febbc62476","tid":1956324,"uid":147784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T08:49:36.000Z","msg":"手土"},{"pid":"146075d08bd1aa384faf9c267d925b3836f13748","tid":1956324,"uid":69074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T08:50:57.000Z","msg":"有用post先推"},{"pid":"ce7e133a4e695def5e26d0d54f6cb4f8308ca542","tid":1956324,"uid":236414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cb2c51682cec093d9bc3fb3a0ef3f004b58ae10b","tid":1956324,"uid":131691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"665feb7a82390065ec9b3d7dac40bf81701436df","tid":1956324,"uid":236414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,